nand the valley, \nand the land, \nand the sea, \nand the island, \nand the meadow where mention of God \nhath been made, and His praise glorified.","name":"Blessed is the Spot","translations":[{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bla","lang_name":"Blackfoot"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"km","lang_name":"Central Khmer"},{"language":"km","lang_name":"Central Khmer"},{"language":"chr","lang_name":"Cherokee"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gwi","lang_name":"Gwich'in"},{"language":"gwi","lang_name":"Gwich'in"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"hur","lang_name":"Halkomelem"},{"language":"hur","lang_name":"Halkomelem"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Hawaiian"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Hawaiian"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"ga","lang_name":"Irish"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kiw","lang_name":"Kiwai"},{"language":"lkt","lang_name":"Lakota"},{"language":"lkt","lang_name":"Lakota"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"lut","lang_name":"Lushootseed"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"moh","lang_name":"Mohawk"},{"language":"meu","lang_name":"Motu"},{"language":"nv","lang_name":"Navajo"},{"language":"pap","lang_name":"Papiamento"},{"language":"pap","lang_name":"Papiamento"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"fa-translit","lang_name":"Persian (Latin)"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"slh","lang_name":"Sliammon"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"BH11209","text":"Gee Kayne dah mah zon, Ke shay Manito, che ke kayne ne me nan, Shegwah che mah wim we to nan, Che mean e ge e ze yan. Che ke kayne ne me nan ke kaye da ma zon ke zong e ze win she quah neen aye pee chee nay. sou e ze yan, shegwa ka a pe chee we note e ze yun. She gwah neen apee chee ke tee mak e ze anne. Keen aye ta go ka Manito win, ka we che tas so win, Apee saig e ze an, kah ke kay kah ah ya yin.\n\n* I bear witness, O my God, that Thou hast created me to know Thee and to worship Thee. I testify, at this moment, to my powerlessness and to Thy might, to my poverty and to Thy wealth.\nThere is none other God but Thee, the Help in Peril, the Self-Subsisting.","name":"Short Obligatory Prayer","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"am","lang_name":"Amharic"},{"language":"am","lang_name":"Amharic"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar-translit","lang_name":"Arabic (Latin)"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"A